}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The FCC test report lists an additional model of CBW560E.
"PN:2PB-CB5600-A00R" and "2008-05-21" is silkscreened on the main board in the FCC photos.
"613A200064R" and "BCM94318MPG" is silkscreened on the wireless module, which is marked as a WL5011S w/ FCC ID of D6XWL5011S ([[Tecom WL5011S]]). The FCC ID of this device has been assigned to this entry.
The default crednentials (cable:''blank'') are from the FCC manual.
